Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.88,0:24:34.81,Preview2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Foi exilado do Shinsengumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.81,0:24:39.81,Preview,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8}Contudo, como todo Otaku perdedor,
